{
  "stem": "21482.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And every morning, he would decide that he has to teach us a lesson, so that we would be either witnesses to public hangings or executions or people just would be taken out and just beaten.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, a real sadistic killer, a real sadistic killer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Just enjoyed killing innocent people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was that first day, that first-- the end of the day, the first day, when those who were sent to clean the ghetto came back.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] In the ghetto, little children were murdered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Some of the children were just thrown from the roof, the little ones.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the other-- some of the people were-- and children-- were put on trucks and sent to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Sam, the head of the Jewish police, with his wife and children-- one of his daughter was married, she was pregnant-- but 60 people were brought to Plaszow and were killed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Right up on another hill in camp, that's where they--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They remained because they were supposed to liquidate it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after it was all liquidated, they thought-- maybe some of them thought they would save themselves because they carried the orders of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, of course, once they did what they were told to do, they were brought and, you know, shot at the edge of the hill over there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of people were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was then that we realized nothing was going to really save us, nobody was going to save us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we couldn't imagine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think people still always had hope.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The war was going on and the German would lose, but the Germans were winning everywhere and making steps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just couldn't imagine what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
